trans-unit.source: Specifies the properties that are in a <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Anger de egenskaper som är i ett <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A StylusPointDescription specifies which properties are associated with a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>.
trans-unit.target: En StylusPointDescription anger vilka egenskaper som är associerade med en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: For each property in a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>, the StylusPointDescription contains a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo> object which specifies constraints such as the minimum and maximum values of the property.
trans-unit.target: För varje egenskap i en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>, StylusPointDescription innehåller en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo>objekt som anger begränsningarna, t.ex de lägsta och högsta värdena för egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A> methods to check for these properties in the StylusPointDescription.
trans-unit.target: Använd den <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A>metoder för att söka efter de här egenskaperna i StylusPointDescription.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: All <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint> objects in a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> must share the same StylusPointDescription.
trans-unit.target: Alla <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>objekt i en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection>måste dela samma StylusPointDescription.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: If you try to add a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint> to a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> that has a different StylusPointDescription, an exception will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Om du försöker lägga till en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>till en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection>som har en annan StylusPointDescription, genereras ett undantagsfel.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor creates a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription> that contains information for the properties <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.X>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.Y>, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.NormalPressure>.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktorn skapar en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription>som innehåller information för egenskaperna <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.X>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.Y>, och <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.NormalPressure>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.NormalPressure> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.Y> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.X> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription>

trans-unit.source: You must pass in <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo> objects for the properties, <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.X>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.Y>, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointProperties.NormalPressure>.
